    • chiral sourcing tied to same boundary structure via Π M_{2,3}

Temperature:
    a_{ℓm}^{T,Π} ∼ γ_Π ⟨ Y_{ℓm}, Π M_{2,3} ⟩

Polarization:
    a_{ℓm}^{B,Π} ∼ ε_Π ⟨ {}_2Y_{ℓm}, Π M_{2,3} ⟩
